1. In Person sample: Builder is inside Person class as a static class;
2. Person only has private constuctor;
3. Person's fields are get from builder;
4 New Person are create by calling Person's build function, in which a new builder instance is created. 

5. Pay attention of following fucntion: 

public People.Builder phone(String val){
			this.phone= val;
			return this;
		}
		
6. To create new instance, we actually start from creating a new Builder		




Key Point: 

a. static builder class;
b. builder self populate function;
c. build() is in Builder;
d. private People constructor
e. static get instance function in People